## Third-Party Libraries

This project uses the following open-source libraries:

### JavaScript Libraries
- **MQTT.js** (MIT License) - MQTT client library for JavaScript
- **Chart.js** (MIT License) - For data visualization (if used)

### Python Libraries  
- **paho-mqtt** (Eclipse Public License 1.0) - Python MQTT client
- **requests** (Apache 2.0) - HTTP library for Python

### Arduino Libraries
- **PubSubClient** (MIT License) - MQTT library for Arduino/ESP32
- **DHT sensor library** (MIT License) - Adafruit DHT sensor library
- **BH1750** (MIT License) - BH1750 light sensor library
- **ArduinoJson** (MIT License) - JSON library for Arduino

### Flutter Packages
- **flutter** (BSD 3-Clause) - Google's UI toolkit
- **material** (BSD 3-Clause) - Material Design components

### Assets & Resources
- **Material Icons** (Apache 2.0) - Material Design icons
- **Cupertino Icons** (MIT License) - iOS-style icons

