## Disclaimer

This software is provided for educational and demonstration purposes only. 
When working with hardware components and electrical connections:

- Always follow proper safety procedures
- Verify all connections before powering on
- Use appropriate protective equipment
- Consult qualified professionals for complex installations
- The authors assume no responsibility for any damages or injuries

For production use, ensure proper security measures are implemented including:
- TLS/SSL encryption for MQTT communications
- Strong authentication mechanisms  
- Network security configurations
- Regular security updates and monitoring